    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Retro Dungeon Slayer》是一款复古风格的第一人称射击（FPS）地下城探索游戏，在程序生成的地下城中与怪物作战。挥舞剑刃，发现强力升级，并在致命生物的波涛中为生存而战！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/48efe630b358492c9e3669a3cc627b03.avif?t=1772361215\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.poster.avif?t=1772361215\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.webm?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/c1f25bba6fd8534043878294ccfbb148.mp4?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《Retro Dungeon Slayer》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Retro Dungeon Slayer》是一款复古风格的第一人称射击类地牢探索游戏，采用像Minecraft一样的像素美术风格。玩家探索程序生成的地下城，与致命的怪物对抗，并选择武器进行生存战斗。游戏提供快速节奏、充满动作的战斗，兼具怀旧感和现代感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/b2c1f5b0b9e1f9ebb4af767f918c98b3.avif?t=1772361215\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.poster.avif?t=1772361215\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.webm?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304930/extras/1f855164c148fe876a828758c59db31c.mp4?t=1772361215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Retro Dungeon Slayer》的每一次挑战都是独一无二的，要求玩家在选择武器时策略性强，并能够适应不断变化的地下城布局。游戏中有超过10种敌人和激烈的BOSS战斗，玩家必须保持警觉才能生存下来。游戏着重于可重玩性、动态战斗和持续的挑战，使每次游戏都充满冒险。</p>",
